│ all users of the instructions in `InsertedInstructions` are either in the `InsertedSet` or │
│ are explicitly handled as exceptions.\n\n5. **Conclusion**: The fix involves ensuring that │
│ the `InsertedSet` is correctly populated and maintained throughout the expansion process.  │
│ This will prevent the assertion failure and ensure that the cleanup process works as       │
│ intended."})                                                                               │
